text: Lucien Degauchy (born June 11, 1937) is a member of the National Assembly of France from 1993 to 2017. He represented the Oise department, and is a member of the Union for a Popular Movement. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
